title: Mossfire Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Mexican, Southwestern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hummus, green chile soup, vegetarian taco salad, black bean enchiladas, tempeh tacos, tempeh burritos, tempeh burger, hummus wrap, veggie melt sandwich, vegetarian black beans, and vegetarian cilantro lime rice. Many items can be vegan by ommitting the cheese. The red chile vinegarette dressing is vegan.
